@baseUrl = http://localhost:8020
@apiKey = dev-demo-key

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Governance knowledge style query
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: analyst@contoso.com
X-Role: viewer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "What is the policy for privileged role assignments?",
  "context": {
    "source": "teams-chat"
  }
}

### Non-sensitive action
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: operator@contoso.com
X-Role: operator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "Create task to review inactive guests and notify owners",
  "context": {
    "tenant": "contoso"
  }
}

### Sensitive action should pause for approval (operator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: operator@contoso.com
X-Role: operator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "Disable compromised account and revoke sessions",
  "context": {
    "ticket": "INC-4421"
  }
}

### Sensitive action as admin (allowed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: admin@contoso.com
X-Role: admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "Disable compromised account and revoke sessions",
  "context": {
    "ticket": "INC-4421"
  }
}

### Audit logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow/audit?limit=20
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: admin@contoso.com
X-Role: admin
